<span id="freeTextContainer1109922888036060542">Loved this book, read it in 2 sittings, and the twists and turns in the plot kept me intrigued all the way. Calli and Petra are two little girls, best friends, who both go missing in the night time, from their separate homes. Ben is Calli&apos;s brother who would do anything for his little sister. As we move through this heart wrenching tale, trying to find out where the girls are, and if they are still alive, we learn about the other characters in the book. <br/>Well worth a read, it&apos;ll draw you in.....</span>
  <span id="freeText1109922888036060542" style="display:none">Loved this book, read it in 2 sittings, and the twists and turns in the plot kept me intrigued all the way. Calli and Petra are two little girls, best friends, who both go missing in the night time, from their separate homes. Ben is Calli's brother who would do anything for his little sister. As we move through this heart wrenching tale, trying to find out where the girls are, and if they are still alive, we learn about the other characters in the book. <br />Well worth a read, it'll draw you in.....</span>
